The '''Solusar family''' was a [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitive]] family of [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knights]]. Its known members included [[Ranik Solusar]], [[Kam Solusar]], and his wife [[Tionne Solusar|Tionne]].

